responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "B9572B5C40EE03BBDA2D6D85583A6EC3", "Hail Citizen! Please leave the swordplay to the Tower Guard. Protecting the roads is our specialty. If help you must then seek out our lost lumber wagons. We can\'t build defenses without lumber!")
